reflected the $1.48billion decrease in underwriting margins (including the unfavorable impacts of an increase in catastrophes and a decrease in net favorable prior year reserve development)
from 2011. the change in income tax expense in 2011 from 2010 was also impacted by the $76million benefit in 2011 resulting from the favorable resolution of various prior year tax matters.
