average credit rating of the $893million and $1.05billion of non-guaranteed cmo holdings at december31, 2012 and 2011, respectively, was "b2" and "ba1,"
respectively. the average credit rating of all of the above securities was "a1" and "aa3" at december31, 2012 and 2011, respectively.
at
